Ansible is an open-source automation tool used for configuration management:

application deployment, 
task automation, and 
IT orchestration. 

It simplifies complex tasks and streamlines processes by using a declarative language to describe system configurations.

Ansible Architure
* it is an Angent less tool 
Ansible must be install in only Master machine 

