Pre-request of Ansible machines
* SSH ===> Connetivity must ====> Master & Slave machines
* Python must be installed in both machines


==> Default file
* Ansible maintain a default inventory file /etc/ansible/host

Ansible host file
* it default disable the servers hosts
## [webservers]
